{"type": "article", "id": 57587, "title": "一把很酷的电动牙刷，纯黑哑光色系外加极简造型｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-10-23T22:41:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53667, "name": "TID Watches"}, {"id": 45517, "name": "Form Us With Love"}, {"id": 53668, "name": "Infiniti"}, {"id": 21855, "name": "Harkavy Furniture"}, {"id": 51432, "name": "Buzzispace"}, {"id": 53669, "name": "Goby"}, {"id": 53670, "name": "Philippe Tabet"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 181, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181023144613OGNA5uLYyofIh7nt.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Monochrome Toothbrush by Goby </h3><p>2015 年成立的 Goby，是电动牙刷领域的生力军。它号称拥有比多数市面上的竞品更出色的洁净效率，其秘密就在它的刷头上面，采用了专利的“旋转振荡”技术，可迅速将牙齿上的牙菌斑、牙垢彻底清除掉。</p><p>Goby 近期推出了一款纯黑配色的单色牙刷，看起来像是一款酷酷的医用工业产品，每个细节，都勾勒出极简主义的样貌，且内置了定时功能，配置了哑光黑色系的充电底座，每月只需要充电两次。如果我们使用的牙刷也能成为表达自我个性的一部分，那么 Goby 算得上是一个美丽而聪明的解决方案。售价 60 美元，<a href=\"https://www.goby.co/products/electric-toothbrush-all-black\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145439kT6Wi5KcJB23NP1p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231454394OFPND0zYSvIJnus.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145439cwXJrhSueVz59QFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145440WCm4t1qB2USkljx7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.861875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Buzzibracks by Alain Gilles for Buzzispace</h3><p>在本周的 2018 德国科隆国际办公家具展上，比利时设计师 Alain Gilles 为 Buzzispace 推出了新的办公家具解决方案 Buzzibracks。</p><p>比利时品牌 Buzzispace 成立于 2007 年，专注于办公环境的改善，既有对美学的探索，也有对噪音的控制。此番推出的 Buzzibracks 系列，强调声音和光线对于人们工作环境的重要性。</p><p>一个个模块化单元系列，可以划分大型工作空间，使用户能够成为他们自己办公空间的架构师，随时调整办公区域以满足任何需求。它由薄而黑的独立框架组成，并配有窗帘，窗帘可以选择多种颜色。此外，Kvadrat 面料提供透明或不透明的选项，以更加适合某些空间和功能。除此之外，模块化设计还可以配备一系列附加装饰，比如台面，挂钩和存储配件。</p><p>该设计的柔软结构不仅可以作为视觉分离遮挡物，还可以作为声学分隔板。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145547yZ9B4YISvrOTQ6Jm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145548u1Xaw4T32HSP9hK0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145547VbhOzq0Fg8dDM3ZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145548sodfDexuhAW8cLHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231455489KbhgzYljEQMB4pX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231455491PrTMAYDmZENCVKH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145549HZf4QEDiwGKuRL72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://buzzi.space/stories/orgatec2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Buzzispace</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Sling Collection by Harkavy Furniture</h3><p>Harkavy Furniture 是一对兄弟几年前在波特兰创立的家具品牌，其特色是通过使用实木和钢材创作出线条简洁利落的家具。其最新作品是 Sling 系列桌子，框架采用手工制作的胡桃木制成，顶部为粉末涂层钢制表面，中间的收纳层为黑色手工缝制皮革面料。</p><p>木材、金属和皮革的融合，整体带来干净简约的感觉，同时突出材料的原始美感。Sling 系列的每个元素都是可定制的，包括硬木的选择，粉末涂层颜色以及皮革或帆布吊带材料的选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145730qUGDftLvNgp2B8ho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231457297XvgilOKzRUpC3JP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145730rbENa2CGDho6uP35.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505963\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145730CZ7srbIKdgaLGkMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231457313QAksE0IFLMc19fZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668750\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145732YUiP3KT78OSp1Qvq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.488333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145733MgLArnF93bwc2hsT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482031\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/sling-collection-harkavy-furniture/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Ruelle Chair by Philippe Tabet for Infiniti</h3><p>最近，法国设计师 Philippe Tabet 为意大利品牌 Infiniti 设计了一款名为 Ruelle 的座椅，将铸铝材质与胶合板结合在一起。Ruelle 在法语中是“小巷”的意思，在设计师看来，现代都市人忙着在工作的间隙逃离城市喧嚣，往往都会去特意找寻那些巷子中的小酒馆，这些小酒馆中大多摆满了这种极具特色与代表性的餐椅。</p><p>Ruelle 座椅试图重新诠释出法国小酒馆常见座椅的重要元素中的内核精神，外形上体现在或宽或窄的靠背，着重表现形态的优雅与柔和，使得铸铝零件与胶合板的融合成为了可能。座椅可多个堆叠，还有户外版本可供选择，户外版本配备塑料靠背和带孔座面，方便座椅在餐厅户外区和露台使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818pavAqtIhYBicxPu6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231458181aMDWEpzwPoClIu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818pF0V7v3G4uhHZsB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818pfehl3umqbYMHLVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818ip2v6ucz8DXJd5UC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818pfDI23FgqoUw1M5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818wd6HyDIln2KsgaP0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023145818kGASr0aQuReFC7DV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：nfiniti</figcaption></figure></div><h3>No.1 36 Black Edition by Form Us With Love for TID Watches</h3><p>在智能穿戴式设备横行，移动互联网普及的时代，手表变得越来越复杂了。但其实时间功能真的需要那么复杂吗？瑞典设计师工作室 Form Us With Love 2012 年创立了手表品牌 TID Watches，用极简主义设计风格，呈现出纯粹的时间功能，没有冗余的智能元素，甚至连日期都没有。</p><p>No.1 手表是 TID Watches 的标志性产品，它适用于不同领域、不同风格的受众。最近，Form Us With Love 推出 No.1 的全新 36 Black 版本，一整块不锈钢表壳搭配突出的表耳，整个表面涂有丰富的黑色离子，赋予手表金属雕刻的质感。表盘的纹理大胆、复杂，用明确的压痕代替了数字和指针标识。售价 250 美元，<a href=\"https://www.tidwatches.com/en/shop/black-edition\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231502384n3hdm2Uq6a1MoFb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023150238FDqkMpBQjCbwh0yI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810231502388IA4SNuFcBzGTLya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023150239DCjeqrgUcHTduY9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023150239B46QnSzR9OClhqVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181023150239JGCLn8TXfYdeoulW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}